ire County, Massachusetts|Hampshire County]] (north)\n*[[Worcester County, Massachusetts|Worcester County]] (east)\n*[[Tolland County, Connecticut]] (southeast)\n*[[Hartford County, Connecticut]] (south)\n*[[Litchfield County, Connecticut]] (southwest)\n*[[Berkshire County, Massachusetts|Berkshire County]] (west)\n\n===Communities===\n\n====Cities====\n*[[Agawam, Massachusetts|Agawam]]\n*[[Chicopee, Massachusetts|Chicopee]]\n*[[Holyoke, Massachusetts|Holyoke]]\n*[[Palmer, Massachusetts|Palmer]]\n*[[Springfield, Massachusetts|Springfield]] (traditional county seat)\n*[[West Springfield, Massachusetts|West Springfield]]\n*[[Westfield, Massachusetts|Westfield]]\n\n====Towns====\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n*[[Blandford, Massachusetts|Blandford]]\n*[[Brimfield, Massachusetts|Brimfield]]\n*[[Chester, Massachusetts|Chester]]\n*[[East Longmeadow, Massachusetts|East Longmeadow]]\n*[[Granville, Massachusetts|Granville]]\n*[[Hampden, Massachusetts|Hampden]]\n*[[Holland, Massachusetts|Holland]]\n*[[Longmeadow, Massachusetts|Longmeadow]]\n*[[Ludlow, Massachusetts|Ludlow]]\n*[[Monson, Massachusetts|Monson]]\n*[[Montgomery, Massachusetts|Montgomery]]\n*[[Russell, Massachusetts|Russell]]\n*[[Southwick, Massachusetts|Southwick]]\n*[[Tolland, Massachusetts|Tolland]]\n*[[Wales, Massachusetts|Wales]]\n*[[Wilbraham, Massachusetts|Wilbraham]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n====Census-designated places====\n*[[Blandford (CDP), Massachusetts|Blandford]]\n*[[Chester (CDP), Massachusetts|Chester]]\n*[[Holland (CDP), Massachusetts|Holland]]\n*[[Monson Center, Massachusetts|Monson Center]]\n*[[Russell (CDP), Massachusetts|Russell]]\n*[[Wilbraham (CDP), Massachusetts|Wilbraham]]\n\n====Other unincorporated communities====\n{{div col}}\n*[[Bondsville, Massachusetts|Bondsville]]\n*[[Depot Village, Massachusetts|Depot Village]]\n*[[Feeding Hills, Agawam, Massachusetts|Feeding Hills]]\n*[[Three Rivers, Massachusetts|Three Rivers]]\n*[[Woronoco, Massachusetts|Woronoco]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n====City neighborhoods====\nThe following are neighborhoods located in Springfield or West Springfield.\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n*[[Bay, Springfield, Massachusetts|Bay]]\n*[[Boston Road, Springfield, Massachusetts|Boston Road]]\n*[[Brightwood, Springfield, Massachusetts|Brightwood]]\n*[[East Forest Park, Springfield, Massachusetts|East Forest Park]]\n*[[East Springfield, Springfield, Massachusetts|East Springfield]]\n*[[Forest Park, Springfield, Massachusetts|Forest Park]]\n*[[Indian Orchard, Springfield, Massachusetts|Indian Orchard]]\n*[[Liberty Heights, Springfield, Massachusetts|Liberty Heights]]\n*[[McKnight, Springfield, Massachusetts (and Mason Square)|McKnight]]\n*[[Memorial Square, Springfield, Massachusetts|Memorial Square]]\n*[[Merrick, West Springfield|Merrick]]\n*[[Metro Center, Springfield, Massachusetts|Metro Center]]\n*[[Old Hill, Springfield, Massachusetts|Old Hill]]\n*[[Pine Point, Springfield, Massachusetts|Pine Point]]\n*[[Six Corners/Maple Heights, Springfield, Massachusetts|Six Corners and Maple Heights]]\n*[[Sixteen Acres, Springfield, Massachusetts|Sixteen Acres]]\n*[[South End, Springfield, Massachusetts|South End]]\n*[[Upper Hill, Springfield, Massachusetts|Upper Hill]]\n{{div col end}}\n\nThe following are neighborhoods located in Chicopee.\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* Aldenville\n* Burnett Road\n* Chicopee Center (Cabotville)\n* Chicopee Falls\n* Fairview\n* Smith Highlands\n* Westover\n* Willimansett\n{{div col end}}\n\nThe following are neighborhoods located in Holyoke.\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[Churchill, Holyoke, Massachusetts|Churchill]]\n* Downtown\n* [[Elmwood, Holyoke, Massachusetts|Elmwood]]\n* [[The Flats, Holyoke, Massachusetts|The Flats]]\n* [[Highlands, Holyoke, Massachusetts|Highlands]]\n* [[Highland Park, Holyoke, Massachusetts|Highland Park]]\n* Homestead Avenue\n* [[Ingleside, Holyoke, Massachusetts|Ingleside]]\n* Jarvis Avenue\n* [[Oakdale, Holyoke, Massachusetts|Oakdale]]\n* [[Rock Valley, Holyoke, Massachusetts|Rock Valley]]\n* 